-- RBS Hires Ex-Dresdner Banker McIntyre to Head Corporate Finance
-- B y   G r a n t   S m i t h
-- 2010-10-31T12:18:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-31/rbs-to-hire-former-dresdner-banker-john-mcintyre-times-reports.html
Royal Bank of Scotland Plc has hired
 John McIntyre , previously head of mergers and acquisitions at
Dresdner Kleinwort Group Ltd., as head of its corporate finance
business in Europe, the Middle East and Africa, spokeswoman
Aoife Reynolds said by telephone from London today.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story:
Grant Smith in London at 
